{{#extend "layout"}}

    {{#content "intro"}}
        {{#if model.components.intro}}
            {{> (lookup model.components 'intro')}}
        {{/if}}
    {{/content}}


    {{#content "main"}}
        <div class="page-header">
            <h1>{{model.title}}</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">

                {{#if model.components.content}}
                    {{> (lookup model.components 'content')}}
                {{/if}}

                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                        <h3>Location</h3>
                        <div class="thumbnail">
                            <div class="thumbnail-img-content">
                                <img src="/images/about/facilities/location-v1.png" class="img-responsive"/>
                            </div>
                            <div class="thumbnail-content">
                                <div>
                                    <p>We are located in the Valley of Cwmdulais, just outside Pontardulais, Swansea. It
                                        is sometimes called Rhododendron valley and it is at its most beautiful in the
                                        spring when all the rhododendrons are in full bloom.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                        <h3>Training Fields</h3>
                        <div class="thumbnail">
                            <div class="thumbnail-img-content">
                                <img src="/images/about/facilities/training-fields-v1.png" class="img-responsive"/>
                            </div>
                            <div class="thumbnail-content">
                                <div>
                                    <p>Our training fields are extensive and they all offer panoramic views of the
                                        surrounding countryside. We have a wide variety of agility equipment for all
                                        sizes of dogs that is great fun for the owner to use with their dog.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                        <h3>Parking</h3>
                        <div class="thumbnail">
                            <div class="thumbnail-img-content">
                                <img src="/images/about/facilities/parking-v1.png" class="img-responsive"/>
                            </div>
                            <div class="thumbnail-content">
                                <div>
                                    <p>We have ample parking areas for many cars.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                        <h3>Indoor Training</h3>
                        <div class="thumbnail">
                            <div class="thumbnail-img-content">
                                <img src="/images/about/facilities/indoor-training-v1.png" class="img-responsive"/>
                            </div>
                            <div class="thumbnail-content">
                                <div>
                                    <p>We have a large training barn to enable the training to continue when the weather
                                        is inclement, for safety the floor is covered with sand for a soft landing when
                                        the dogs are playing.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                        <h3>Shop</h3>
                        <div class="thumbnail">
                            <div class="thumbnail-img-content">
                                <img src="/images/about/facilities/shop-v1.png" class="img-responsive"/>
                            </div>
                            <div class="thumbnail-content">
                                <div>
                                    <p>We also have a shop that sells high quality training equipment such as leather
                                        training leads and collars, buying here ensures that you are trained correctly
                                        by experts how to use the equipment.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                        <h3>Hospitality Cabin</h3>
                        <div class="thumbnail">
                            <div class="thumbnail-img-content">
                                <img src="/images/about/facilities/hospitality-cabin-v1.png" class="img-responsive"/>
                            </div>
                            <div class="thumbnail-content">
                                <div>
                                    <p>We have a log cabin that is a hospitality area, and we are able to sit in comfort
                                        and warmth when having a discussion about your dog.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <a href="{{ model.next.link }}" class="btn btn-primary">Next: {{ model.next.name}} </a>

            </div>
        </div>
    {{/content}}

{{/extend}}
